表格异常记录的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('ErrDataInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table ErrDataInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: ErrDataInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table ErrDataInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
MachineNo varchar(12) not null,
MouldNo varchar(12) not null,
DispatchNo varchar(20) null,
WorkOrderNo varchar(12) not null,
OriginalData varchar(200) not null,
ModifyData varchar(200) not null,
UploadDate datetime not null,
ModifyFlag bit not null,
InputFlag bit not null,
Operator varchar(20) not null,
OperatorDate datetime not null,
constraint PK_ERRDATAINFO_2 primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
